This R Markdown document presents a comparative study on testing [the KOMPUTE imputation algorithm](https://github.com/statsleelab/kompute) with data from [the International Mouse Phenotyping Consortium (IMPC)](https://www.mousephenotype.org/). The analysis spans two versions of IMPC data, namely version 16 and version 10.1, across three phenotyping domains: Body Composition, Clinical Chemistry and Open Field. 

## IMPC Data Version 16
* [Example 1) Body Composition data](kompute_test_BC_v16.html)
* [Example 2) Clinical Chemistry data](kompute_test_CC_v16.html)
* [Example 3) Open Field data](kompute_test_OF_v16.html)
